items.text: Foie gras: 10 points!!
The Kong Bak Pau I liked! Thick cuts of pork belly that has been stewed! I liked that it was not overly spiced! Try it!
Crab is good!!!
Happened to come across this drinks promotion (applicable on Facebook) while we were seated at the table facing this notice written at one of the pillar 😃
Don't bother coming here, the service suck and the food are mediocre. Ordered their black angus beef and it's not bad. The rest are just blah.
Try the garlic crab
what to eat
The Foie Gras satay is almost melt in your mouth!!! 😍
My favorite restaurant in Singapore hands down. The fried beef is a must. Egg yolk squid is also great as is the foie gras skewer. Jumbo sri lankan crabs are great--regular crabs mediocre.
Another one of my favorites here 😊 Fragrant sambal with a good balance of acidity from the Assam 👍👍👍
Salted egg crabs, chicken/pork satay, black angus beef steak and the durian can boleh! (creme brûlée)
Must try their steak which comes with a beef fried rice too !
Angka prawn with salted egg, lamb rack & heart attack rice with Angus beef are excellent
don't order the steak + rice. it's all mine!
Tucked away in the middle of an industrial estate but really worth the trek. Fantastic crab, good steak and the beef rice is dangerously good.
Give this a skip to make room for other things ... Oyster Omelette with huge huge oysters !!!
The crab beehoon and pork knuckles shldnt be missed! Don't go for the prawn-paste fried chix tho...
X'mas promo.. 2 + 1 seafood promo...
They moved from Sin Ming but the food was still great. Try their ribeye steak.
This is a gem in the midst of car repair shops. Their lamb is perfectly grilled and tender. Try their shovelnose ray head for something unique.
This dish has to be preordered as it takes 60mins to slow-cook. The taste is simple yet rich .. Even the salt used has deeper tones than normal. The taste of the egg is juxtaposed with the liver 😍
expensive?
Fish Roe !! Was ok but was better before 😊
Buy two crab , and get one more free :) lotsa flavor to choose how you want do your crab ! Salted egg yolk, chili, black pepper .. Cream sauce, and more :)
For directions, look for the lighted crab sign amidst the sea of car workshops
The worst. All the food came cold. Must say the angus was quite tender though cold, but tastes like it has been pounded. Crab Beehoon, brinjal all bad. Boss Beehoon passable but no ingredients
corkage free all week
crabs ... buy 2 get 1 ... yum yum
Been here twice & the food never fails. Try the foie gras in this photo and you will love it! Salted egg dishes are winner!!!
The Angus Beef Platter is also a MUST EAT!! We ordered 2 in the end ... It's abt $75+ a platter!
Must order "boss bee hoon" and crispy fried eggplant
Parking could be a problem. Park near Block 26 and walk to the restaurant. They allow BYO as in u can bring your own wines even tho they have cellars full 😝
The name is ironic. Avoid the seafood & dive face first into the BBQ pork ribs, steak & amazing fried rice & the chicken pot pie
Mee Goreng not great either ... Was overly charred (wok hei gone wrong)... No spice ... No kick! No need to order this.
The Garlic butter crab is yummy. The garlic was fantastic
Amazing seafood and meat dishes. Squid in salted egg yolk! Foie Gras on slowly poached egg!
Order the steak and that's all
외식계의 백화점. 다판다. 크랩도 점보나 노싸인보드보다 훌륭
Maybe too much MSG... Was super thirsty and had pounding headache afterwards...
Steak. Satay.
Garlic baked crab is different and mild, but yummy. Steamed baby squid is yum! Brinjal delight also a winner!
their signature bbq pork ribs, salted egg prawns, and the huge pork knuckles!
Salted egg prawns/crab is da bomb! Have to agree, the pork knuckle is pretty good too.
The food is excellent. You have to try the prawns cooked and encrusted with salted eggs. It is delicious.
BYO savvy !! Able to Bring - Your - Own wines. Best of all , they have the necessary wine glasses for your needs.
Deep fried baby squid alright but better at Jumbo. Almost everything else I've tried is awesome
The food here is great!! The chilli crab, bee hoon and the pork is a must to eat. Trust me.
Believe it or not but go here for the steaks. Trust me
This salted egg crab is one of the better ones I've tried . Good flavor, not too salty & not oily ... Hopefully the next time will be exactly the same 👍👍👍
Want wine with your food but unsure which wine is good? Check out their wine pairing recommendations on the blackboard out front. Of course ... they'll have those bottles on their menu.
Good food, reasonable price and free corkage
Must eat!! The small plate is $12. Tasty!!
Discovered an old favourite: chai por (chopped preserved turnip) hor fun. Full of wok hei (breath of the wok)!
Order the Steak. Trust me
Mmmmmmmmm ribs
Food standards have been dropping each time I visit :( Might not return !
Incredible seafood for a place with great steak. Incredible steak for a place with great seafood. Cheap good wine. Must have: crab, salted egg squid, flower clams, STEAK.
That fish egg dish, man, unforgettable! There are bucket lists and last meal lists. Put this on both. If I could only remember the name of it.
Everything is yummy. Reservation is a challenge.
Salted egg squid is too heavy. Deep fried brinjal is crispy and not bad
Beef steak, crab
Crowded place with many regular customers, remember to call to make reservation few days to a week earlier, especially for weekends dinner.
Food is great and I would recommend friends. But huge caveat: they use MSG here. You will be very thirsty after eating here.
Smoke pork rice taste not very nice. I like the burn smell of Hokkien noodle and love the  foie gras w egg
Must have steak, pork knuckles and garlic baked crabs!
Every dish at ubin seafood is just damn good !!! Yes .. Crabs, steak, pork ribs, Claypot chicken, deep fried baby squids, beef fried rice & more .. spoilt for choices indeed !! :)
The flavour of this Tze Char restaurant's version of Prawn Paste Chicken ( 虾酱鸡 / Har Cheong Gai ) is just nice and tender meat soft enough for me to chew. Delicious :-9
Crayfish is excellent
The beef fried rice is an accompaniment to the Angus Beef Platter - it comes whether u can stomach it or not! It's fried with the beef fat and taste like claypot rice.
Foei grais on sticks and the steak is a must have!
Very crowded during weekends. Better reserve or risk making a fruitless trip. Seems to be the IT restaurant in this area.
lamb n hokkien mee
Salted egg crab 👍🏼 crab beehoon soup is a miss though...
The Ubin Fried Rice is good
Ribeye steak yeah. And of course the crabs.
Good service here !
Pork knuckle & Fried Hokkien Noddle are must try !!
New item ! Foiegras + sodt boiled egg ! Yum !! A cuppa to start ! Nice !
Food is served cold nowadays...😓
Must try the Angus Beef set - beef, and fried rice 👍
The baked spare ribs tasted as if they were baked slowly... Very tender and the BBQ sauce was served on the side if u need more....
The baked garlic crabs are a tasty and healthier alternative to the rest.
Surprisingly delicious fusion tze char. Loved the cereal prawns, har cheong gai and salted egg crab. Special mention for the excellent beef steak!
Buy 2 crab get 1 free!
Seafood is not the only thing they serve here. The non seafood dishes are awesome, especially the ribeye and lamb rack. They serve oysters too.
Beef steak, garlic crab!!
Had the signature beef and fried rice, curry fish head, supreme ribs, nai bai vege and salted yolk prawns. Beef is juicy and tender. Fish head is fantastic though you hardly see any recommendations.
Pork Knuckle is overrated. Steak is very good and rest of dishes are of standard.
Must try the roasted beef and onions!
Beef steak & fried rice!!!!
Used to be better
Avoid Seafood! Try steak and rib.
Hokkien mee, foie gras w egg is what I like
EVERYTHING IS AWESOME!
Steak is great
The crispy shrimp didn't cause fireworks to occur. Like eating prawn keropok!
Must try the salted egg crab!
Skip seafood and go for the kurobuta Pork ribs
OMG! Delicious lamb steak is tender and easily chewable or cuttable by metal spoon 😍👍👍 Eventhough its at S$7 per piece, but its flavour and texture is done much nicer than many other restaurants.
Too awesome food here? The satay foie gras is really crazily awesome
If your purchase two crabs, you get another free. However, the quality of crabs here has unfortunately worsened over the last few years.
This Tze Char restaurant's version of 三色蛋 (assorted eggs) in broth comes with Spinach, Mushroom and Wolfberries. Its colourful and nice. I like :-)
5 mutton 5 pork - give this a miss to make room for other dishes !!! 😁
The beef platter is surprisingly good for a seafood Resturant
Delicious pork knuckle, hk style live marble goby. However give the kl style hokkien noodles a miss, way too heavy on the salt
This fried eggplant is a must try!
Shifted from Sin Ming to Bukit Batok end of 2016
Love the beef steak with potatoe wedges n fried rice, fried brinjal, crab braised beehoon n hk Kai lan. Yums.
Food is ok but service sucks big time the guy taking the order got serious attitude problem
Beef steak and black peeper crab are highly recommended
What to order: pork ribs, knuckles, beef steak cubes, satay, mee goreng. Best ALL ROUNDER restaurant!
I love the beef
Overheard: "They have two dishes you must have: 1) The grilled steak along with the fried rice that they fry in the steak fat. HOLY COW! 2) The boss bee hoon."
Super yummy US Black Angus Ribeye Steak with fried rice, wedges & onions !! $12.00 per 100 gram 👍👍 - no 1 selling dish !
The salted egg crab dish is wicked. So is the sambal oyster omelet. Really like the background music choice. When I was there, it was New Orleans jazz. :))
steak and har jiong gai. fried brinjal and salted egg squid wasnt fantastic
Salted egg fried oyster and rib eye steak must try!
BBQ beef med rare among the better items on the menu. There's also a wine selection though there's no corkage if you byo
My son loved this dish - Fried Fish Roe with Chincalok and Petai...
Beef and onions was succulent.
Grossly overpriced. Can get MUCH BETTER steak elsewhere for the ridiculous price. Snooty service. Plus for all the hoops u have to jump through to get a reservation, completely upsetting
The steak is surprisingly good!
